Use the standard library
This is how to remove_vowels of text:
   Remember that vowels is "aeiouAEIOU"
   Remember that result is ""
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this text's length times:
      Remember that c is item i in text
      When c is not in vowels, then:
         Add result to c
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
